Package model

Class MyEngine

java.lang.Object
framework.Engine
model.MyEngine
public class MyEngine extends Engine
Main simulator engine. Demo simulation case: Simulate three service points, customer goes through all three service points to get serviced --> SP1 --> SP2 --> SP3 --> SP4

    • findShortestQueue

      public ServicePoint findShortestQueue(ArrayList<ServicePoint> servicePointArr)
      Finds the Service Point that the Customer is put into: either takes the first shortest one, or in case of queue sizes being the same, picks a random Service Point
      Parameters:
      servicePointArr - ArrayList of Service Points that the ServicePoint should be from
      Returns:
      Service Point with either the shortest queue or a random one if shortest can't be found

    • handleArrival

      public void handleArrival(Event t)
      Handling of ARRIVAL event. If associated Customer has done online Check-In, places them to Security, updates their target position; if not, places them to Check-In, updates their target position. Generates next arrival event.
      Parameters:
      t - The event that is being handled
      Throws:
      IllegalStateException - if the target position for the assigned queue cannot be determined.

    • tryCEvents

      protected void tryCEvents()
      C-Phase Events: checks through every ServicePoint in the system and checks if they're currently free and if there is someone in the queue. If so, ServicePoint's beginService() method is called.
      Specified by:
      tryCEvents in class Engine

    • setAllCustomerPercentages

      public void setAllCustomerPercentages(double onlineCheckInCustomers, double innerEUCustomers, double businessClassCustomers)
      Sets all Customer related percentages at once. Note that values should be between 0-100.
      Parameters:
      onlineCheckInCustomers - percentage of customers checking in online (skipping on-site check-in)
      innerEUCustomers - percentage of customers traveling inside of EU (skipping Border Control)
      businessClassCustomers - percentage of business class customers (put in fast track security)

    • setAllTimingMeans

      public void setAllTimingMeans(double arrival, double checkIn, double borderControl, double security, double boarding)
      Set all timing means at once
      Parameters:
